    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209920/extras/aef8c056b48507e52e816a713d80dfb5.poster.avif?t=1748870673\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209920/extras/aef8c056b48507e52e816a713d80dfb5.webm?t=1748870673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209920/extras/aef8c056b48507e52e816a713d80dfb5.mp4?t=1748870673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bathhouse Creatures is a small and cozy management game about running bathhouses for silly talking animals. Serve quirky animal guests, upgrade your bathhouse facilities, uncover heartfelt, wholesome stories and watch your bathhouse grow to be the best it can be!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build &amp; Manage Your Bathhouse</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring an old and abandoned bathhouse back to it's former days of glory! Place bathtubs, purchase decorations, and upgrade facilities to attract the local folk to come and soak their stresses away. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209920/extras/845ee6ba2ffb16dc89b5651b73de4dec.poster.avif?t=1748870673\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209920/extras/845ee6ba2ffb16dc89b5651b73de4dec.webm?t=1748870673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209920/extras/845ee6ba2ffb16dc89b5651b73de4dec.mp4?t=1748870673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Serve Lovable Animal Folk</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare warm and soothing baths for the local animal folk. Stay on your toes and decorate the bathhouse according to their preferences to keep them happy and satisfied. Use delectable treats and tasteful décor for extra payments and rave reviews!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209920/extras/c601f6abf0287401c064faa7a63d91ea.poster.avif?t=1748870673\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209920/extras/c601f6abf0287401c064faa7a63d91ea.webm?t=1748870673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209920/extras/c601f6abf0287401c064faa7a63d91ea.mp4?t=1748870673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Get To Know Your Guests</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn about the whimsical creatures that patronize your bathhouse, ranging from ducks to capybaras. Each level will serve as a backdrop to wholesome short stories for you to learn about each guests' hopes and worries. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209920/extras/57ed81a247c87c3a257094d89af432b7.poster.avif?t=1748870673\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209920/extras/57ed81a247c87c3a257094d89af432b7.webm?t=1748870673\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3209920/extras/57ed81a247c87c3a257094d89af432b7.mp4?t=1748870673\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-3 hours of story gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Serve baths for your guests by making sure tubs are filled and warmed by your fire-breathing dragons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play each level strategically to complete each animal's story and  objectives</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn about your animal guests coming from all walks of life, such as Ruck the mischievous Duck, Hana the elderly Capybara, or Hugo from the notorious Hippopota-mafia!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate your rooms with bathhouse items such as rubber ducks, cherry blossom plants, hot springs banners, and even a katana display...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy upgrades for your tubs such as dragon training or magical filtration systems!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
